criteria.textblock:
        Inclusion Criteria:

          -  Schizophrenia following DSM IV;

          -  Age 18-57;

          -  Stability of the clinical state;

          -  Ability to learn;

          -  Deficit in intention reading as measure with the V-SIR (V-LIS in French) test (score
             >13);

          -  informed consent to participate to the study.

        Exclusion Criteria:

          -  Any other organic or neuropsychiatric disease
